; Coverage test for history.cc
; Tests multi-hop price resolution through the price graph.
; multi-hop price path where prices must be chained
; last_target tracking through the price graph path
; inverted price when commodity matches source
; source == target early return

P 2024/01/01 EUR 1.10 $
P 2024/01/01 GBP 0.85 EUR
P 2024/01/01 CHF 0.90 EUR

2024/01/10 Buy
    Assets:European           100 EUR
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Buy
    Assets:British            50 GBP
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Buy
    Assets:Swiss              200 CHF
    Assets:Cash

test bal -X '$' --now="2024/02/01"
                   0  Assets
              $46.75    British
            $-354.75    Cash
             $110.00    European
             $198.00    Swiss
--------------------
                   0
end test
